        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The ascription of praise to God by the representatives of the creation, viz., the four beasts, is joined by that of the twenty-four elders, the representatives of redeemed humanity;[1824] yet here the praise of the elders (",
        "children": []
