        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " sq.,—but to the power and glory of God revealed in creation, so that the words of the elders stand in beautiful harmony with the praise of the four beings, as well as with the significance of the entire vision; of course not without the relation expressly indicated in ",
        "children": []
      },
